-- Israeli Planes Strike Gaza Target in Response to Rocket Attacks, Army Says
-- B y   G w e n   A c k e r m a n
-- 2010-12-21T17:17:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-21/israeli-planes-strike-gaza-target-in-response-to-rocket-attacks-army-says.html
Israeli warplanes struck a target in
the Gaza Strip that the army said was a “Hamas terror activity
center.” The army spokesman’s office said in an e-mailed
statement that the air strike was in response to rocket attacks
on Israel’s southern towns and cities over the past week.  To contact the reporter on this story:
